    "start_blocks": "// Full 100-password spray list\nvar passwordList = [\n  \"123456\", \"password\", \"123456789\", \"12345678\", \"12345\", \"1234567\", \"qwerty\",\n  \"111111\", \"123123\", \"abc123\", \"password1\", \"1234\", \"iloveyou\", \"1q2w3e4r\",\n  \"admin\", \"letmein\", \"welcome\", \"monkey\", \"football\", \"princess\", \"dragon\",\n  \"sunshine\", \"master\", \"654321\", \"qwertyuiop\", \"superman\", \"passw0rd\",\n  \"qazwsx\", \"trustno1\", \"hello\", \"freedom\", \"whatever\", \"charlie\", \"aa123456\",\n  \"123qwe\", \"qwe123\", \"michael\", \"shadow\", \"jessica\", \"asdfgh\", \"hottie\",\n  \"ginger\", \"jordan\", \"maggie\", \"pepper\", \"nicole\", \"hunter\", \"batman\",\n  \"baseball\", \"soccer\", \"cheese\", \"computer\", \"mickey\", \"donald\", \"pokemon\",\n  \"starwars\", \"harley\", \"george\", \"summer\", \"tiger\", \"ashley\", \"qwerty123\",\n  \"test123\", \"liverpool\", \"biteme\", \"daniel\", \"joshua\", \"michelle\", \"love\",\n  \"zxcvbnm\", \"taylor\", \"bailey\", \"snoopy\", \"matthew\", \"cookie\", \"asdf1234\",\n  \"bubbles\", \"patrick\", \"buster\", \"bandit\", \"killer\", \"william\", \"barney\",\n  \"cowboy\", \"tennis\", \"thomas\", \"internet\", \"andrew\", \"orange\", \"merlin\",\n  \"samsung\", \"yamaha\", \"nintendo\", \"steelers\", \"jennifer\", \"thunder\", \"flower\",\n  \"purple\", \"scooter\", \"turtle\", \"phoenix\", \"matrix\", \"google\", \"skittles\"\n];\n\n// Submit button logic\nonEvent(\"button1\", \"click\", function() {\n  var username = getText(\"text_input1\");\n  var password = getText(\"text_input2\");\n\n  if (username == \"z_eriK@example.com\" && password == \"cowboy\") {\n    hideElement(\"button1\");\n    hideElement(\"button2\");\n    hideElement(\"password_list\");\n    hideElement(\"text_area2\");\n    hideElement(\"text_area5\");\n    showElement(\"spraying_explanation\");\n    showElement(\"access_granted\");\n    hideElement(\"spraying_result\");\n    setText(\"spraying_result\", \"✅ Access Granted: Successful login.\");\n  } else {\n    showElement(\"text_area5\");\n  }\n});\n\n// Spray attack simulation logic\nonEvent(\"button2\", \"click\", function() {\n  setText(\"text_input1\", \"z_eriK@example.com\");\n  showElement(\"spraying_result\");\n  var output = \"Spraying password list for user z_eriK@example.com:\\n\\n\";\n\n  for (var i = 0; i < passwordList.length; i++) {\n    var pwd = passwordList[i];\n    if (pwd == \"cowboy\") {\n      output += \"✔ \" + pwd + \"  ← Match found!\\n\\n\";\n      output += \"✅ Success: Password spray attack worked!\";\n      break;\n    } else {\n      output += \"✖ \" + pwd + \"\\n\";\n    }\n  }\n\n  setText(\"spraying_result\", output);\n});\n",
    "start_html": "<div id=\"designModeViz\" class=\"appModern clip-content\" data-radium=\"true\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 450px; display: none;\"><div class=\"screen\" tabindex=\"1\" data-theme=\"millennial\" id=\"screen1\" style=\"display: block; height: 450px; width: 600px; left: 0px; top: 0px; position: absolute; z-index: 0; background-color: rgb(254, 219, 208);\"><input id=\"text_input1\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 235px; height: 40px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(254, 219, 208); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 2px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 65px; top: 127px;\" placeholder=\"username\"><input id=\"text_input2\" style=\"margin: 0px; width: 235px; height: 40px; border-style: solid; color: rgb(68, 44, 46); background-color: rgb(254, 219, 208); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; border-width: 2px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 65px; top: 185px;\" placeholder=\"password\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level8/user (6).png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://user (6).png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"icon1\" style=\"height: 35px; width: 45px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 15px; top: 130px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level8/logo3.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://logo3.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"logo1\" style=\"height: 100px; width: 100px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 10px; top: 10px; margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level8/key.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://key.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"icon2\" style=\"height: 35px; width: 45px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 15px; top: 190px; margin: 0px;\"><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"password_list\" style=\"width: 265px; height: 385px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 230); color: rgb(68, 44, 46); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 325px; top: 45px; margin: 0px;\">123456<div>password</div><div>123456789</div><div>12345678</div><div>12345</div><div>1234567</div><div>qwerty</div><div>111111</div><div>123123</div><div>abc123</div><div>password1</div><div>1234</div><div>iloveyou</div><div>1q2w3e4r</div><div>admin</div><div>letmein</div><div>welcome</div><div>monkey</div><div>football</div><div>princess</div><div>dragon</div><div>sunshine</div><div>master</div><div>654321</div><div>qwertyuiop</div><div>superman</div><div>passw0rd</div><div>qazwsx</div><div>trustno1</div><div>hello</div><div>freedom</div><div>whatever</div><div>charlie</div><div>aa123456</div><div>123qwe</div><div>qwe123</div><div>michael</div><div>shadow</div><div>jessica</div><div>asdfgh</div><div>hottie</div><div>ginger</div><div>jordan</div><div>maggie</div><div>pepper</div><div>nicole</div><div>hunter</div><div>batman</div><div>baseball</div><div>soccer</div><div>cheese</div><div>computer</div><div>mickey</div><div>donald</div><div>pokemon</div><div>starwars</div><div>harley</div><div>george</div><div>summer</div><div>tiger</div><div>ashley</div><div>qwerty123</div><div>test123</div><div>liverpool</div><div>biteme</div><div>daniel</div><div>joshua</div><div>michelle</div><div>love</div><div>zxcvbnm</div><div>taylor</div><div>bailey</div><div>snoopy</div><div>matthew</div><div>cookie</div><div>asdf1234</div><div>bubbles</div><div>patrick</div><div>buster</div><div>bandit</div><div>killer</div><div>william</div><div>barney</div><div>cowboy</div><div>tennis</div><div>thomas</div><div>internet</div><div>andrew</div><div>orange</div><div>merlin</div><div>samsung</div><div>yamaha</div><div>nintendo</div><div>steelers</div><div>jennifer</div><div>thunder</div><div>flower</div><div>purple</div><div>scooter</div><div>turtle</div><div>phoenix</div><div>matrix</div><div>google</div><div>skittles</div><div><br></div></div><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"text_area2\" style=\"width: 285px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgba(254, 234, 230, 0); color: rgb(68, 44, 46); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 320px; top: 10px; margin: 0px;\">100 Most Common Passwords:</div><button id=\"button1\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 40px; width: 95px; background-color: rgb(68, 44, 46); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 20px; border-width: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 65px; top: 245px;\">Submit</button><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level8/company_text1.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://company_text1.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"image4\" style=\"height: 60px; width: 240px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 75px; top: 65px; margin: 0px;\"><button id=\"button2\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 40px; width: 95px; background-color: rgb(222, 72, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 20px; border-width: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 200px; top: 245px;\">Spray Attack</button><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea design-mode-hidden\" id=\"spraying_result\" style=\"width: 280px; height: 110px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 230); color: rgb(68, 44, 46); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 25px; top: 320px; margin: 0px;\"></div><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/test-ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson3-level8/access_granted.png\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://access_granted.png\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"access_granted\" style=\"height: 80px; width: 240px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 335px; top: 55px; margin: 0px;\" class=\"design-mode-hidden\"><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea design-mode-hidden\" id=\"spraying_explanation\" style=\"width: 260px; height: 275px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgb(254, 234, 230); color: rgb(68, 44, 46); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 330px; top: 130px; margin: 0px;\"><br><div>Spraying is a cyber attack where hackers try a few very common passwords (like \"123456\" or \"password1\") across many accounts, hoping that someone is using an easy-to-guess password. </div><div><br></div><div>Instead of guessing one person’s password, they try the same password on lots of users.</div></div><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea design-mode-hidden\" id=\"text_area5\" style=\"width: 285px; height: 35px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgba(254, 234, 230, 0); color: rgb(230, 31, 47); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 8px; border-width: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 45px; top: 290px; margin: 0px;\">Username or password are incorrect.</div></div></div>",
    "long_instructions": "## Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Scroll through the list of the 100 most common passwords in use.\r\n\r\n2. Click the `Spray Attack` button to run a script that tries each of the most common passwords for a specific user.\r\n\r\n3. Review the output window of the Spray Attack. Find the `username` and `password`, enter them into the input boxes, and click the `Submit` button to gain access to this site.",
    "preload_asset_list": null
  },
  "published": true,
